                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6345" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0991</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8772 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“好想你”转让“百草味”：百年好合的联姻为何会解体？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Haoxiangni&quot; Sells &quot;Baicaowei&quot; : Why the Marriage of A Hundred Years of Good Match Disintegrates?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李金茹，单坤月，杨思琦，李天天，韩岩，梁若函，赵天泽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">好想你健康食品股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">好想你；百草味；企业并购；资产重组</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Haoxiangni; Baicaowei; M &amp; A; assets reorganization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016年8月，红枣领军品牌“好想你”以9.6亿元完成对休闲食品“百草味”的收购。联姻期间“百草味”为“好想你”贡献8成的营业收入。2020年6月，“好想你”以50亿元的价格将“百草味”全部股权转让给百事饮料。百年好合的联姻为何会解体呢？本案例以“好想你”与“百草味”联姻后解体为线索，重点描述了百年好合的联姻的动因，联姻期间相互成就，最后联姻解体的过程，并对解体的原因进行猜想，对解体后“好想你”未来发展的挑战进行罗列。本案例旨在为企业并购与资产重组敲醒警钟。同时，学生通过案例学习也将深刻理解资产并购与重组风险把控与会计处理的难题。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In August 2016, the leading brand of red dates &quot;Haoxiangni&quot; completed the acquisition of the leisure food &quot;Baicaowei&quot; with 960 million yuan. &quot;Baicaowei&quot; contributed 80% of the operating income to &quot;Haoxiangni&quot; during the marriage. In June 2020, &quot;Haoxiangni&quot; transferred all the equity of &quot;Baicaowei&quot; to Pepsi beverage with 5 billion yuan. Why does a century-old marriage break up? Based on the clue that &quot;Haoxiangni&quot; and &quot;Baicaowei&quot; disintegrated after their marriage, this case focuses on describing the motivation of century-old marriage, the process of dissolution of the final marriage and the mutual achievements during marriage, inferring the motives of &quot;Haoxiangni&quot; to dispose of &quot;Baicaowei&quot;, as well as the challenges of the future development after the disintegration of &quot;Haoxiangni&quot;. This case aims to keep enterprises vigilant in M&amp;A and assets reorganization. At the same time, through case study, students will also deeply understand the problems of risk control and accounting treatment of asset M &amp; A and reorganization.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业并购与重组》《财务会计理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业进行并购应考虑的财务风险；丧失控制权下处置子公司的会计处理；资产重组的定义、方式及动因；与企业财务绩效有关的指标</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-06</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
